 & = & \frac{1}{T}\Big(nc-\frac{3na}{b}\ln\Big(\frac{V+nb}{V}\Big)\Big(\frac{-1}{2}\Big)T^{-3/2}\Big)=\frac{1}{T}\Big(nc+\frac{3na}{2b}\ln\Big(\frac{V+nb}{V}\Big)T^{-3/2}\Big)\\
